    \title Configure development tools

    Configure development tools for devices in \preferences > \uicontrol Devices.
    The available tools vary depending on the device type and enabled plugins.

    \image {qtcreator-preferences-devices-desktop-tools.webp} {Tool configuration options for a desktop device}
    \caption Tool configuration options for a desktop device in the Devices
    tab in Devices preferences.

    To configure tools for a device:

    \list 1

        \li Go to \preferences > \uicontrol Devices > \uicontrol Devices.

        \li Select an existing device from \uicontrol Device.

        \li In \uicontrol {Type Specific} > \uicontrol {Run tools on this device}
            or \uicontrol {Source and build tools on this device}, specify the paths
            to the tools.

            Or, in \uicontrol {Auto-detection}, configure the auto-detection options
            and then select \uicontrol {Run auto-detection now}.

    \endlist

    \sa {Use Qt Creator variables}, {Build and Run}{How To: Build and Run},
